#: ../../source/api/world_manager_layout.md:1
msgid "World > Camera > Docking"
msgstr "World > Camera > Docking"

#: ../../source/api/world_manager_layout.md:3
msgid ""
"Use `world.camera.add_right(...)`, `world.camera.add_bottom(...)`, and "
"`world.camera.switch_world(...)` as the public API for docking and "
"switching helper worlds."
msgstr ""
"Verwende `world.camera.add_right(...)`, `world.camera.add_bottom(...)` "
"und `world.camera.switch_world(...)` als öffentliche API zum Andocken und"
" Umschalten von Hilfswelten."

#: ../../source/api/world_manager_layout.md:7
msgid ""
"The class below is the internal helper that implements this behavior "
"behind the public camera API."
msgstr ""
"Die folgende Klasse ist der interne Helfer, der dieses Verhalten hinter "
"der öffentlichen Kamera-API implementiert."

#: ../../source/api/world_manager_layout.md:10
msgid "API Reference"
msgstr ""

#: miniworlds.worlds.manager.layout_manager.LayoutManager:1 of
msgid ""
"LayoutManager handles the positioning and management of World objects "
"within an application window."
msgstr ""

#: miniworlds.worlds.manager.layout_manager.LayoutManager:3 of
msgid ""
"It is stored internally on `world._layout`, while the public API is "
"exposed via `world.camera` and delegates layout behavior to the "
"underlying `App` and `WorldsManager`."
msgstr ""
"Es wird intern unter `world._layout` gespeichert, waehrend die "
"öffentliche API ueber `world.camera` bereitgestellt wird und das Layout-"
"Verhalten an `App` und `WorldsManager` delegiert."

